==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Antichlor
<hw>An"ti*chlor</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>anti-</ets> + <ets>chlor</ets>ine.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Any substance (but especially sodium hyposulphite) used in removing
the excess of chlorine left in paper pulp or stuffs after
bleaching.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Antichrist</ent>⟦br⟧
